    <h1>Characteristics</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>A sync of the type <strong>Characteristic</strong> allows you to import characteristics. Characteristics are old properties that are linked at the item level. Imported data is saved in the <strong>Settings » Item » Properties</strong> menu.</p>
</div>
</div>
